* Two career opportunities / types :
     => offensive (red team) - ethical hacking,Attack.
     => defensive (blue team) - SOC(Security Operational Center)Analytics,Reverse enginnering,Malware experts
     => (purple team) - mixer of both red and blue team
* types of hackers:
     => White hat - complete architecture/technology given to the attackers.
     => Black hat - 0% knowledge about the architecture.
     => Grey hat - both the white and black hats(mrgn legal and night illegal)
